Western Digital Corp said itplans to call for redemption on April 6 all of itsapproximately 47 mln dlrs principal amount of 6-3/4 pctconvertible subordinated debentures due 2011.    It said the debentures will be redeemable for 1,090.94dlrs, including accrued interest, for each 1,000 dlrs principalamount.    The debentures will be convertible into Western Digitalcommon stock up until the redemption date at a conversion priceof 17.50 dlrs per share, the company also said. Reuter&#3;